    "body": "This is not a hardening specific flag, it should be used at all times, regardless of if hardening is enabled or not. Note that this was still the case here, but having this exist in the hardening flags is confusing, and may lead someone to move it inside one of the `use_hardening` blocks, where it would become unused, with `--disable-hardening`.\r\n\r\nNoticed while reviewing https://github.com/hebasto/bitcoin/pull/32#discussion_r1363564161.",
